00:07:58.800 --> 00:08:06.800
The point in verse 14 is that if we're conscientious and reach the heart of our Bible students,

00:08:06.800 --> 00:08:13.800
that may be what gives them the needed fortitude to withstand an unexpected trial.

00:08:13.800 --> 00:08:17.800
